OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fwarm evening with late sunshine. Skies
OL,7,Fwill cloud over through the night with
OL,8,Fsome outbreaks of rain in the early
OL,9,Fhours, turning heavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy at first in the morning
OL,12,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,13,FTurning drier through the day with
OL,14,Fincreasing amounts of sunshine.
OL,15,FFeeling much fresher than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
