OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FNot
OL,6,Ffeeling as humid in the new week.
OL,7,FLargely dry with sunny spells, but a
OL,8,Ffew showers possible at times,
OL,9,Fparticularly on Tuesday. Light winds.
OL,10,FFeeling pleasant in the sunshine.
